<section class="py-80 px-8 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h3 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-12 leading-none tracking-tighter">
      Pronto para a <br /><span class="text-primary italic">solução certa?</span>
    </h3>
    <p class="font-body text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface-variant mb-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-80">
      Vamos conversar sobre como a tecnologia pode servir ao seu propósito, não o contrário.
    </p>
    <button class="group relative px-16 py-8 rounded-full font-bold text-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 inline-flex items-center gap-6">
      <span class="relative z-10 text-on-primary">Falar com o Luan</span>
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined relative z-10 text-on-primary group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-container group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
      </div>
    </button>
  </div>
</section>
